ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectConvention for the Avoidance of Double Taxation with respect to Taxes on Income and Capital - Serbia ** RATIFICATION **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification, the Convention between Canada and the REPUBLIC OF SERBIA for the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION WITH RESPECT TO TAXES ON INCOME AND ON CAPITAL.
